parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating
the vehicle fails to shift into gear
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly when in park or neutral
the transmission warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter cable bushing can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly when in park or neutral, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The shifter cable bushing is loose or detached
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly when in park or neutral
the gear shifter is difficult to shift or sticks
the vehicle fails to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the powertrain control module can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating
the vehicle fails to shift into gear
the powertrain control module warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while driving
often without warning
and may restart after a short period. The vehicle may stall at low or high speeds
and the issue may occur repeatedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission problems can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle may jerk or hesitate while shifting gears
and the transmission may slip or fail to engage properly. The issue may occur at low or high speeds
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system malfunctions can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system may malfunction
causing issues with the touchscreen
air conditioning
and heating systems. The issue may occur randomly and without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failures can cause the vehicle to lose control and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal may feel hard or spongy
and the vehicle may take longer to stop than expected. The issue may occur at low or high speeds
and the vehicle may vibrate or pull to one side when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Recall issues can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle may have outstanding recalls that have not been addressed
including issues with the transmission shift cable
Takata airbags
and other components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch system failures can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal may feel soft or spongy
and the vehicle may have difficulty shifting gears. The issue may occur at low or high speeds
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience issues with the brakes, airbags, and other safety features, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
loses power
or experiences issues with the brakes
airbags
and other safety features; the dashboard lights and gauges malfunction; the radio and other electrical components shut off or malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and gearbox can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or experience difficulty shifting gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or experiences difficulty shifting gears; the gearshift sticks or becomes difficult to operate; the vehicle jerks or surges forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of airbags and other safety features can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light does not illuminate upon startup; the airbags fail to deploy in an accident; the blind spot detection system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brakes fail to engage or are difficult to operate; the brake pedal feels spongy or soft; the vehicle experiences complete brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the instrument cluster and gauges can make it difficult for the driver to operate the vehicle safely.
symptoms: The speedometer
tachometer
or other gauges malfunction; the dashboard lights and gauges flicker or shut off; the instrument cluster displays incorrect information.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the windshield wiper and defroster systems can reduce visibility while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The windshield wipers fail to operate or operate erratically; the defroster system fails to clear the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive oil consumption can cause the engine to stall or shut off while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's oil level drops rapidly
requiring frequent oil additions
and may cause the engine to stall or shut off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or shutting off while driving can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or shuts off while driving
often without warning
and may be accompanied by a loss of power steering and brakes.
